 Q.  You already lost two quarterfinals to Milos this year.  What was different tonight?  
GAÃL MONFILS: I think I change a little bit my game plan, you know.  I've been, for sure, more solid today than the previous matches played against him.   
I think I pick up a little bit more first serve, be able to play better from the baseline myself.  I guess I had some opportunities, and tonight I just made them.   
