GAÃL MONFILS: Well, I guess I have fun.  I think tonight I have fun.  For me it was fun tonight.  I always have fun, you know.   
If one day I have no fun, I stop my career straightaway because I'm still the same.  So differently, but if one day I don't want to play tennis, I think I'm one of the players I can say, I stop.  Easy.   
